ttps://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186780/extras/71e82ba6d091c5ccdef7aaf66eb6b7f9.webm?t=1727090554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186780/extras/71e82ba6d091c5ccdef7aaf66eb6b7f9.mp4?t=1727090554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Face off with several alien types. Those aggressive little beasts try to take down you and your ship and will not stop until defeated.",
